'''米洛·吉勃遜'''（{{lang-en|Milo Gibson}}，{{bd|1990年|11月16日}}）是一名美國男演員，[[梅爾·吉勃遜|梅爾·吉勃遜]]的兒子。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/milo-gibson-people-say-i-look-like-my-dad-i-wish-zpk9v5ndd |title=Milo Gibson: People say I look like my dad. I wish! |first=Ed |last=Potton |date=2018-09-06 |work=[[泰晤士报|Times]] |access-date=2021-03-15 |archive-date=2019-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226172722/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/milo-gibson-people-say-i-look-like-my-dad-i-wish-zpk9v5ndd |dead-url=no }}</ref>知名作品如電影《[[鋼鐵英雄|鋼鐵英雄]]》（2016年）、《[[黑幫之地|黑幫之地]]》（2017年）、《{{le|闯入逃离|Breaking & Exiting}}》（2018年）及《{{le|惡魔突襲隊|All the Devil's Men}}》（2018年）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/reviews/all-the-devils-men-review-1203083837/ |title=Film Review: 'All the Devil's Men' |first=Dennis |last=Harvey |date=2018-12-07 |work=Variety |access-date=2021-03-15 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205093118/https://variety.com/2018/film/reviews/all-the-devils-men-review-1203083837/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
米洛·吉勃遜出生於澳大利亞，主要在美國[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[马里布_(加利福尼亚州)|馬里布]]成長<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metro.news/five-things-to-know-about-milo-gibson/1337413/ |title=Five things to know about… Milo Gibson |website=Metro Newspaper UK |access-date=2021-03-15 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204202222/https://www.metro.news/five-things-to-know-about-milo-gibson/1337413/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是[[梅爾·吉勃遜|梅爾·吉勃遜]]和羅賓·摩爾（{{lang|en|Robyn Moore}}）的兒子。他在參與演藝事業前是名[[電工|電工]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/milo-gibson-talks-breaking-acting-best-advice-dad-mel-gibson-1135157 |title=Milo Gibson Talks Breaking Into Acting and the Best Advice He Got From Father Mel |first=Lauren |last=Huff |date=2018-08-17 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=2021-03-15 |archive-date=2021-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327023538/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/milo-gibson-talks-breaking-acting-best-advice-dad-mel-gibson-1135157 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

吉勃遜的首部表演作品為父親電影《[[鋼鐵英雄|鋼鐵英雄]]》（2016年）<ref name= "Hurricane">{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/milo-gibson-world-war-ii-drama-hurricane-fighter-pilot-1202518451/ |title=Milo Gibson to Star in World War II Drama 'Hurricane' |first=Dave |last=McNary |date=2017-08-08 |work=Variety |access-date=2021-03-15 |archive-date=2021-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210105133/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/milo-gibson-world-war-ii-drama-hurricane-fighter-pilot-1202518451/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年在《[[黑幫之地|黑幫之地]]》中主演[[艾爾·卡彭|艾爾·卡彭]]。2018年，他在波蘭和英國合拍的傳記戰爭片《{{le|颶風行動：303中隊|Hurricane (2018 film)}}》中飾演{{le|約翰·A·肯特|John A. Kent|約翰·A·肯特中尉}}<ref name="Hurricane"/>。

